      "Text": "Security update for the Linux Kernel (Live Patch 37 for SLE 12 SP3)",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for the Linux Kernel 4.4.180-94_138 fixes one issue.\n\nThe following security issue was fixed:\n\n- CVE-2021-20322: Make the ipv4 and ipv6 ICMP exception caches less predictive to avoid information leaks about UDP ports in use. (bsc#1191790)\n",
